http://aflcio.org:80/estatements/feb95/attack/attack.html 204.127.237.106 19970215055720 text/html 30310
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.1
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 05:57:00 GMT
