<DOCHDR>
http://aflcio.org:80/issues/docs/ippoor-6er.html 204.127.237.106 19970215091515 text/html 11760
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.1
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 09:14:56 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 22-Jan-97 14:42:36 GMT
